• Service workflow: Step‑by‑step hot‑swap SOPs for crew and drones, with pass/fail checks.
• Pattern library: Beacon, lighthouse, tree, crest, and “Earth stories” presets with safe power/thermal budgets.
• Manufacturing BOM: Component list, standardized tile footprints, and refurbish loop guidelines.


